From: Arnaldo Carvalho de Melo <acme@redhat.com>
Date: Wed, 28 May 2025 12:53:08 -0300
Subject: Revert "perf thread: Ensure comm_lock held for comm_list"
Git-commit: 24bcc31fc75b760e7813e1c8257a7439e045e8ad
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

This reverts commit 8f454c95817d15ee529d58389612ea4b34f5ffb3.

'perf top' is freezing on exit sometimes, bisected to this one, revert.

